com.danielly.jsf.cinema.services.admin

Class MovieAdmin

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.danielly.jsf.cinema.services.admin.MovieAdmin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Named(value="movie_data")
 @RequestScoped
public class MovieAdmin
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Class MovieAdmin provides methods to manage the movies in the GUI interface. It handle the inputs, query the database and notify the user when needed.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Gil Danielly
